Percent mortality per day computed during the reservoir timestep i.

Done by splitting the reservoir into two parts: spill side and power side based on -spill. Then the integration routine simpson_2d() is called. If the TDG saturation is less thn the critical value on both sides of the river, than a much simpler routine to compute mortality base_gas_mort() is called.

Returns:
Percent mortality per day during reservoir timestep i
